---
title: Roasted Veggie & Plant-Based Pesto Penne with Basil & Plant-Based Parmesan
description: We're adding layers of flavour to this easy pasta dish by roasting veggies and then tossing them into a rich sauce with basil pesto.
The veggies caramelise in the oven and develop lightly charred edges, transforming your finished dish into a taste sensation!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-vegetble-red-pesto-penne-194ee05d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/roasted-vegetble-red-pesto-penne-61306aec37eb2c28a5330867-35603024.pdf
cuisine: Italian
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/roasted-veggie-and-plant-based-pesto-penne-61306aec37eb2c28a5330867
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
nutrition:
  fat: 22.1 g
  saturated fat: 10.6 g
